<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Crafty" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Crafty,</orth> cunning, sly: <bibl n="shak. ado 3.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 1, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 2.406" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 406</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.504" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 504</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.100" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 2, 100</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.254" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 254</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.254" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 254</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.4.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 4, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.4.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 4, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.1.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 1, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.1.57" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 1, 57</bibl>. <cit><quote>you may think my love was c. love and call it cunning,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 4.1.53" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 1, 53</bibl></cit> (i. e. feigned love; cf. <emph>crafty-sick</emph>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>